{"title":"黄浦江上的回声（外一首）","authors":["莎白"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦江上的回声（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莎白"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，上海港有从工人成长起来的引水员。而解放前上海港的引水权长期落在外国人手里，由外籍人员担任引水员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的海面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的港湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的灯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的声音……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我掂过分量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知道这担子有多重！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人呗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界还要叫它翻个身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这旧的海运史永远过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在，中国工人来引航！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船大？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放胆行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜黑？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里明！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滩浅？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我熟悉每一寸海程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上红云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江上繁星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是上海港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正张开双臂迎客人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我借你的汽笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答祖国一声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杯酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一个退休老工人的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干上这一杯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天可该"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来敬你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机台当磨台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖辈转来转去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前老板说咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生来“草料坯”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“草料坯”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“工人工程师”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只差一辈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不过换了个社会！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱敬你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不为光耀门楣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这“囍”字本该贴在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人大家庭的院内！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呀，你这双手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒全像我的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可上面的老茧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只许加厚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，工程师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干上这一杯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫嫌这酒里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴着爹爹的喜泪！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}